                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable S</hi> 85.) I was at the station when the prisoners and the boots were brought.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Allen's Defence.</hi> I was going up Albany-street, the man took me, and struck me several times; I had nothing about me.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Brook's Defence.</hi> He searched me, and tore my waistcoat open; I had nothing, and he let me go; I went on, Mr. Buer met me, and took me back <hi rend="italic">to</hi> where they were scuffling.</p>
